Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.31,0:00:05.56,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:08.27,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:13.45,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:18.58,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:31.34,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:39.76,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:51.65,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:54.95,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:57.70,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:02.58,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:08.04,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:17.34,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:32.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, another message from the\NSecond Kira was sent to Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:34.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's a video and a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:37.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:40.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A diary? He's moving again.\NThat idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:43.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't he just wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:49.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he want the diary to\Nbe shown on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:51.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:57.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,2006... Last year's diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:00.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at the thirtieth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:05.14,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz4.392\move(290,156,222,156,0,16)}28th There's going to be something\Nbetter coming out than the PZ2, called PZX.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:05.14,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz4.392\move(271,376,202,376,0,16)}30th Confirmed our Shinigami\Nat the home game at the Tokyo Dome
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:04.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Check for Shinigami at the Tokyo Dome...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:08.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure he's saying he wants\Nto do that on May 30...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we air this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the public will find that\Nthat's what he plans to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:16.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:19.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he can't see my Shinigami unless\Nhe touches my notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so how does he plan to do that-?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.74,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(356,356)}22nd My friend and I showed\Noff our notebooks in Aoyama
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:27.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:28.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:33.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I see my own lifespan\Neven if I have the Shinigami eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People who have Death Notes only\Nneed to know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the lifespan of the people they kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:45.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Shinigami can't see\Nthe lifespan of other Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:49.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,people who hold a Death Note\Ncan't see each other's lifespans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:56.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May 22nd, My friend and I showed off\Nour notebooks in Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:00.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If "notebook" means "Death Note,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then it would only be understood\Nby me, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:04.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:07.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will probably pay attention to\Nthe May 30 entry which says,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:11.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"We confirmed our Shinigami\Nat the home game the Tokyo Dome."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:17.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty certain that the "Aoyama" part of\Nthe message is the real message...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't say anything carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should watch how he approaches this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:33.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now...\NI can only say that he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He is, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:38.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious that he wants to\Nmeet Kira at the home game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:41.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he understand that\Nif we air this there'll be a panic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:45.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the game will be canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, it's so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'm not sure how to\Ndeal with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the diary is broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:01.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then we'll have to announce that\Nthe game on the 30th is canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don't, the Second Kira\Nwon't make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he gets angry that\Nwe canceled the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no telling what he'll do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:14.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Second Kira seems to\Nworship Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He promised the Kira we created\Nthat he'd refrain from killing carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:25.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll air the diary and announce\Nthe cancellation of the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:29.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And also announce that we're going\Nto close off and inspect all roads
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,around the Tokyo Dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:36.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, our "own" Kira\Nwill respond with,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Understood. I'll meet you there."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really think that they would\Ngo there even
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if we're inspecting the roads\Naround the dome, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:49.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that the real Kira will go,\Nbut I'm not sure about the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell how stupid he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:54.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:57.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming that he isn't\Nas stupid as we think he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:01.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to see if there might\Nbe another message within this diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a code that\Nonly people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:11.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who have the so-called Shinigami power\Ncan understand, I can't decode it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:17.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we should thoroughly check out\Nthe places listed in the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The 22nd, he's meeting\Na friend in Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The 24th, he's meeting a friend in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to prepare for the possibility\Nthat our efforts will be fruitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We also have to be wary of\Npeople waiting with notebooks in Aoyama
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and people lurking in\Nclothing stores in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:42.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the fake Kira is caught,\NI'll have to obtain his notebook....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:46.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the worst case scenario,\NI may have to kill everyone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:53.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is place more surveillance\Ncameras in Aoyama and Shibuya
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:57.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and station undercover officers\Non the stated dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:01.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go to Aoyama and\NShibuya since I'd fit right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:03.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:09.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Dad. I go to\NAoyama and Shibuya occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:14.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd be the one who'd look\Nmost natural hanging out with Mr. Matsui.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:19.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the only person the Second Kira\Nis interested in is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:27.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mr. Matsui, I'll talk to you tomorrow\Nabout going to Aoyama and Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:30.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Light. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This always happens as soon\Nas I go out and turn on my phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:49.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ryuzaki. Please be sure\Nto watch Light very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep this a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:55.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes... I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's still\Na small percentage of doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we still have\Nto suspect him, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, you're late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to keep the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm helping with\Nthe investigation a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a girlfriend\Nat the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:17.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light has a girlfriend? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, I'm an 18-year-old\Ncollege student...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should work on it too, Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I-I don't have to go\Nfor something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, what about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The room service took care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about a hotel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:42.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?! What was that?!\NA scandalous statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Ryuk...\NI have something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:56.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Shinigami who come to\Nthe human world talk to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm attached to someone,\NI think that's against the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,unless I have the permission\Nof the person I'm attached to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a code\Nagainst that, so I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,another Shinigami might\Nstart talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So does that mean if\NFake Kira's Shinigami sees you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:18.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a chance that\Nhe'll tell the Fake Kira that I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's usually not done,\Nbut it depends on his personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:27.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can just assume that\Nyou'll act how you usually do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:32.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Even if I see someone\Nwith a Shinigami, I won't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think what you're doing is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:39.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:43.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Fake Kira... Have you thought\Nthis out this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:44.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama is pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was searching for ways we\Ncould find each other, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:56.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On the 22nd, there is an event at\Na club called the Note Blue in Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:01.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao means "Blue"...\NAnd "note"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty elaborate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be smarter than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:11.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means I need to be\Nmore careful, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:15.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,right now, this Note Blue\Nis worth checking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:20.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't want him to\Nknow that you're Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:31.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my friends from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pleased to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my cousin Taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:42.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his first time in Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:45.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and he said he wanted to go have\Nsome fun in Aoyama and Roppongi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also looking for a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone want to volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would ever suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a detective within this group of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Ryuk is spotted,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:13.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,no one could tell who he's attached to\Nif I'm with this many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also defense against\NL's surveillance cameras...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not such\Na bad way to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:24.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to watch the entrance\Nof Note Blue when it opens...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:43.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it... Tsuki [Moon]... Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the only one whose\Nlifespan I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:51.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I would\Nfind him so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Rem. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:03.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just found him.\NIs that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:07.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just greet him by saying,\N"Mr. Kira...I'm pleased to meet you,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in a place with all these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know his name.\NI can easily look him up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's such a unique name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.54,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz16.348\pos(490,244)}Born: February 28, 1989
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.54,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz16.348\pos(508,286)}Height: 5 feet 10 ¾ inches
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.54,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz16.348\pos(486,345)}Weight: 119 pounds
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.54,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz16.348\pos(478,401)}Blood Type: A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written as "moon,"\Nbut read as "Light."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is amazing,\Nthis Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He won the national tennis competition
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:45.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when he was in his second and\Nthird year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave an address as the\Nfreshman representative
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,at this year's entrance ceremony\Nat To-oh University...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no picture of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there can't be anyone else\Nwith a name like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:59.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought that Kira\Nwould be so young and cool...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's better than I ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many places that will just go\Nand sell your personal records.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is so twisted, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I even know his address now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a trace of anything\Nhappening in Aoyama
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:18.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on the 22nd and Shibuya on the 24th.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only place left is\Nthe Dome on the 30th...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:25.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see anyone who could\Nbe the Fake Kira at Note Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he really be going\Nto the Dome?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, Sakura TV just received
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,another message\Nfrom the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's postmarked... on the 23rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have found Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:47.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of the people at the television station\Nand the police, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be-!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? In Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:56.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did his Shinigami find\NRyuk and tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... There's no way that he could\Ntell who Ryuk was attached to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I made sure that no one\Nwas following me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:08.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is true, the only thing that\Ncorresponds to this tape
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,being mailed on the 23rd\Nis the 22nd in Aoyama
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda and Light Yagami are\Nthe only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from this investigation\Nwho went to Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Light really Kira-?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have absolute proof\Nthis happened in Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He found him?\NThat's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:28.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... It means that the Second Kira\Nand Kira have teamed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still not sure\Nif they've teamed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Second Kira is only saying\Nthat he found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He may not have contacted him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we've come to this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:46.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the police will have to send\Na message to the Second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Send a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:53.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The police will have to reach out\Nto the Second Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:56.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and offer him a deal in\Nexchange for Kira's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a really bad turn\Nof events?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how the\NFake Kira would react...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no reason to stop this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:16.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira doesn't know who you are yet,\Nthere is still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't approach Kira out of curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will kill you if you contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:25.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll just use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:30.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What you can do is reconsider\Nthe value of human life,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and atone for your crimes by\Ngiving us information on Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and save the people of the world\Nfrom Kira's reign of terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:42.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wonder if it's your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:51.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:01.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.\NMy name is Misa Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:05.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to give Light an important notebook\Nhe left at the university...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could you wait for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Notebook-?! Could it be-?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Misa Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:35.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be worried\Nif you were watching TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't take it any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:50.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami-!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:52.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the Fake Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is it all right-?\NI'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, she came all this way\Nto return my notebook to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you make us some tea\Nor something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I suppose I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one\NI was telling you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:35.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I thought so.\NYou didn't do the eye deal, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have the Shinigami eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:42.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you can see a person's\Nlifespan and age. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:46.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you cannot see the lifespan\Nof someone who has a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:52.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I didn't know that detail...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if you were\Ncaught by the police
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:00.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and Kira's secret was discovered-?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:08.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't caught and if I continue\Nto do as you say, I won't be. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will see L's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will become your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:16.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:19.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So-?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make me your girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:25.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Girlfriend-?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:27.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not careful with her,\Nshe might kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:40.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There were three times\Nthe usual number of surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:46.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone in Aoyama would have\Nbeen caught on camera. Including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we remained together\Nafter that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even being together here isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:59.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a picture of me\Nwhen I went to Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure no one would\Nrecognize her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about your fingerprints-?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:11.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The tapes you sent to the television station\Nall have the same fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't my fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did put some thought\Ninto my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A little while back I lived\Nin the Kansai region.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:21.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a friend who was into the occult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I told her we should\Nmake fake ghost videos and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:28.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,send it to several TV shows,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she agreed to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:33.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had her dub ten tapes and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:36.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I made sure not to leave\Nany fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I took those video tapes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and put the Kira picture on it\Nand added sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is that friend doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to kill her,\NI'll kill her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:51.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really...\Ndon't believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:55.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hold on to my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:59.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just holding on to it,\Nso I'll still have ownership and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll still have my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:05.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's no way\NI can kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:13.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm of no use, you can kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she go this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:20.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you might have removed\Nseveral pages from the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:22.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be hiding them somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so suspicious of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if you just use me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:30.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly one year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:42.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my parents were killed by\Na robber right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:49.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the trial was drawn-out and some people\Nstarted saying he was falsely accused...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:54.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when Kira punished him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira...means everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:05.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just... I just wanted to\Nmeet you so badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:07.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:16.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All these irrational methods\Njust to meet Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But at least she can get\Naround surveillance cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:22.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and keep her fingerprints\Noff the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:24.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not as stupid as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:28.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She even says that she'll obey me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:49.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:53.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be your boyfriend,\Nbut I can act like I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:59.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes you gave up half of\Nyour life for, to meet me and to help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will be a valuable weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:07.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...\NI'll try hard to make you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:28.34,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:33.72,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:42.73,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:49.16,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:53.70,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:59.42,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:06.88,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:12.05,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:22.82,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:28.61,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:37.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:39.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you're a friend I have much\Nin common with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:43.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been lonely since you've been\Ntaking breaks from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:46.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to play tennis with you again.
